## Workflow Chain

<!-- awf:section workflow-chain -->
Follow this canonical chain for feature and fix work:

1. **{{ .prefix }}-brainstorming** — explore intent, surface constraints, pick approach
2. **{{ .prefix }}-proposing-adr** — record significant decisions; ADRs live under `{{ .vars.adrDir }}`
3. **{{ .prefix }}-reviewing-adr** — review the proposed ADR before acceptance
4. **{{ .prefix }}-writing-plans** — write a bite-sized implementation plan; plans live under `{{ .vars.plansDir }}`
5. **{{ .prefix }}-reviewing-plan** — review the plan before execution starts
6. **{{ .prefix }}-reviewing-plan-resync** — re-review after plan adjustments
7. **{{ .prefix }}-executing-plans** / **{{ .prefix }}-subagent-driven-development** — execute tasks one-by-one, gate after each
8. **{{ .prefix }}-reviewing-impl** — review the finished implementation before merge

Never skip steps; each gate keeps later steps cheap.
<!-- awf:end -->

